OL,6,FA care home manager has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of ill-treating and sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting 'vulnerable' residents at a
OL,9,FNorth East care home.
OL,11,FWilliam Malcolm, known as Bill, faced
OL,12,Ften counts of sexual assault, two of
OL,13,Fill treatment of a person in care and
OL,14,Fone of racially aggravated harassment.
OL,16,FHe was accused of abusing his position
OL,17,Fas a registered nurse by committing
OL,18,Fsexual offences against residents at a
OL,19,Fresidential home, which cannot be
OL,20,Fnamed to protect the identities of
OL,21,Fthose affected.
