OL,3,CCare home manager found guilty of ill
OL,4,Ctreatment and sexual abuse of residents
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old, of West Hope Close in
OL,7,FSouth Shields, also faced a charge of
OL,8,Fracially aggravated harassment against
OL,9,Fa colleague and of sexually assaulting
OL,10,Fthree other women who were not
OL,11,Fresidents at the home.
OL,13,FThe court heard how Malcolm was
OL,14,Fracist, homophobic and repeatedly
OL,15,Fkissed and cuddled two vulnerable
OL,16,Fpatients. One colleague described his
OL,17,Fbehaviour to the jury as "disgusting."
