OL,3,CCare home manager found guilty of ill
OL,4,Ctreatment and sexual abuse of residents
OL,6,FWitnesses claimed the defendant had
OL,7,Fdirected foul mouthed personal insults
OL,8,Fat a person in their care about their
OL,9,Fbody and that he had also made
OL,10,Foffensive remarks about the bodies of
OL,11,Ftwo female colleagues.
OL,13,FOne witness had also claimed Malcolm
OL,14,Fwould repeatedly kiss and cuddle two
OL,15,Fvulnerable patients. That same witness
OL,16,Fclaimed to have seen him lean onto the
OL,17,Frocking chair of another woman,
OL,18,Fthrusting his hips close to her before
OL,19,Fshe told him firmly to stop.
